---
description: Workshop quickstarter coding guidelines
globs:
  - apps/streamlit-agent/**
alwaysApply: true
---

- Keep examples simple and runnable.
- Prefer deterministic tools for demos.
- Validate env vars with clear error messages.
- Keep prompts short and explicit.
- Prefer MCP-backed docs/tools when relevant (`docs-langchain`, `shadcn`).
- Add or update smoke tests when behavior changes.
